WEBVTT

00:13:28.362 --> 00:13:30.678
to je bio radar i internet.

00:13:31.129 --> 00:13:33.413
To je bio Tang, piće uz doručak -

00:13:33.437 --> 00:13:36.314
verovatno ne najvažnije od ovih otkrića.

00:13:36.795 --> 00:13:39.674
Ali imali ste partnerstvo i dijalog,

00:13:39.698 --> 00:13:41.963
a dijalog se raspao.

00:13:41.987 --> 00:13:44.366
Raspao se jer se u Vašingtonu smatra

00:13:44.390 --> 00:13:46.156
da što manje upravljate, to bolje

00:13:46.180 --> 00:13:48.659
Raspao se jer u Vašingtonu imamo,
verovali ili ne,

00:13:48.683 --> 00:13:50.523
rat protiv nauke -

00:13:50.547 --> 00:13:53.586
uprkos činjenici
da u čitavoj ljudskoj istoriji

00:13:53.610 --> 00:13:56.570
svaki put kad je neko vodio
rat protiv nauke,

00:13:56.594 --> 00:13:58.195
nauka je pobedila.

00:13:59.463 --> 00:14:04.390
(Aplauz)